        </speech>
        <speech by="#a2ecc3d6-a000-4b2d-9d06-fce8dba1caa9">
          <from>HON. LEONARD PREYRA</from>
          <p>HON. LEONARD PREYRA : Mr. Speaker, before I read my resolution, may I make an introduction?</p>
