        <speech by="#50073f98-101e-4a05-aef5-b6739b325fb8">
          <from>HON. CHARLIE PARKER</from>
          <p>HON. CHARLIE PARKER : I want to move Bill No. 59, An Act to Amend Chapter 3 of the Acts of 1987, the Canada-Nova Scotia Offshore Petroleum Resources Accord Implementation (Nova Scotia) Act to now be read a second time.</p>
        </speech>
        <speech by="#75109949-5b99-4b9c-b9fd-d85a8ce227ab">
          <from>MR. SPEAKER</from>
          <p>MR. SPEAKER : The honourable member for Richmond.</p>
